Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.96,0:01:36.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天氣變暖和了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.03,0:01:38.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.23,0:01:41.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,7號校舍是往這邊走嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.33,0:01:43.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該沒錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.63,0:01:45.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經有一年級新生了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.83,0:01:46.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.84,0:01:53.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(353,266)}在對人關繫上行動選擇的特徵
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.84,0:01:56.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現視研會有新人加入嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.88,0:01:58.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我可不要
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.65,0:02:02.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是現視研熱鬧起來 高阪就更不可能改邪歸正了…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.92,0:02:05.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.15,0:02:06.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.35,0:02:08.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小笑 小笑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.69,0:02:12.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要跟我一起Cosplay去招募新社員呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.93,0:02:14.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs40}絕對不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.83,0:02:18.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底要到什麼時候才肯Cosplay呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.47,0:02:19.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先給我慢著
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.53,0:02:21.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是時間的問題嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.70,0:02:22.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.94,0:02:25.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是不是 絕對不是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.51,0:02:27.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.74,0:02:32.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也正聊到要不要用Cosplay來吸引新社員
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.28,0:02:36.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 用它來代表現視研的活動 似乎太狹隘了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.99,0:02:40.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且也只有兩個人喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.99,0:02:43.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幾乎可說是個人興趣了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.19,0:02:45.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其…其實用什麼方法招募都可以啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.89,0:02:48.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用…用那個來招募社員 似乎太…太強烈了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.23,0:02:52.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目前的氣氛就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.77,0:02:56.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我只要有機會就不想錯過呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.91,0:02:57.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.17,0:03:01.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只要一談到Cosplay 個性就會大變耶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.24,0:03:02.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.64,0:03:04.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果找來什麼怪人 我可不管哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.25,0:03:08.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 這點早就不用當心了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.75,0:03:10.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為早就全是些怪人了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.42,0:03:17.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們不照慣例辦那個第幾回的什麼會議嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.89,0:03:19.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用不著客氣哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.33,0:03:21.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然扯到這裏來了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.87,0:03:26.96,不签,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學生會以外的人士禁止進入
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.04,0:03:28.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原作進入第二部
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.04,0:03:32.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為新角色登場 使得劇情有了重大的轉變
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.21,0:03:33.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但大家也看得津津有味
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.05,0:03:42.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現…現在看到亞力士 還真…真讓人懷念啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.75,0:03:45.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟這在大總集篇中 可是珍貴的新作畫面
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.02,0:03:47.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且演得很熱血
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.46,0:03:59.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼你們能一再重複的看那麼多遍？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.44,0:04:01.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有趣嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.70,0:04:05.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼會問這種最基本的問題呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.14,0:04:07.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要說有趣還是無趣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.81,0:04:09.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然是有趣才會看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.58,0:04:15.38,不签,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無趣的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.62,0:04:17.45,不签,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會長…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.39,0:04:21.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會長！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.69,0:04:23.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會長畢業了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.32,0:04:24.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,離開學校了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.99,0:04:26.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會長？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.89,0:04:28.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.53,0:04:30.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…這麼說來 他怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.77,0:04:31.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.53,0:04:32.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出社會工作？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.67,0:04:34.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或是升上研究所？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.07,0:04:35.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是留級？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.44,0:04:36.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且他到底是幾年級的？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.91,0:04:38.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還在哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.68,0:04:42.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用不著嚇成那樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.41,0:04:44.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 一般人都會被嚇到的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.51,0:04:47.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難不成是做了什麼虧心事嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.35,0:04:49.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 完全沒有！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.29,0:04:52.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來說件能讓你放心的事好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.15,0:04:55.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在此我要宣佈一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.06,0:04:56.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.16,0:05:00.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我打算辭去會長的職位
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.80,0:05:07.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,……這還真是突如其來的重大宣佈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.40,0:05:10.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想也差不多該畢業了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.44,0:05:12.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「差不多」是念了幾年啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.27,0:05:15.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…這表示他到現在都沒打算過要畢業嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.91,0:05:19.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年我打算花一整年時間來專心寫畢業論文
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.45,0:05:21.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,資料也都收集齊全了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.62,0:05:23.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼資料？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.15,0:05:27.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我打算推薦斑目擔任下一任會長
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.99,0:05:29.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.13,0:05:32.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個提議不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.86,0:05:35.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且實際上 你幾乎就等於是會長了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.87,0:05:41.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而…而且 其他四年級的就只剩原口一個人而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.57,0:05:42.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.04,0:05:46.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也老是把社團的實際營運交給田中做了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.54,0:05:49.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那還是先去問問田中比較好吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.78,0:05:51.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就接下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.35,0:05:52.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很適合啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.25,0:05:55.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.55,0:05:56.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.22,0:05:59.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就試試看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.22,0:06:02.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你就是第二任會長 麻煩你了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.12,0:06:04.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二任？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.16,0:06:05.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才第二任？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.53,0:06:06.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且人不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.03,0:06:14.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs28}(因為種種因素 請勿攝影)
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.89,0:06:34.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 通過
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.43,0:06:46.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然有兩個新人要加入啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.23,0:06:48.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說只是暫時加入的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.54,0:06:50.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也還沒見過他們
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.71,0:06:54.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然會有人想加入那種社團啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.51,0:06:56.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道他們會是怎樣的人 真讓人期待啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.42,0:07:09.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你啊什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.76,0:07:11.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.23,0:07:12.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎樣啦？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.46,0:07:18.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正打算要玩的新人大考驗泡湯了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.20,0:07:20.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 新人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.37,0:07:22.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.51,0:07:31.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該先做個自我介紹吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.01,0:07:33.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫澤崎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.28,0:07:35.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敝姓朽木
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.68,0:07:38.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請叫我朽朽～
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.99,0:07:40.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我絕對不會這麼叫你的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.76,0:07:42.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先冷靜點
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.42,0:07:43.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.63,0:07:46.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻煩死了 還是算了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.73,0:07:48.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春日部 你真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.70,0:07:49.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該怎麼說好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.03,0:07:53.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想讓OTAKU知道我的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.57,0:07:56.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 她是普通人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.90,0:07:59.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那她不會玩Cosplay了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.51,0:08:00.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Cosplay？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.68,0:08:02.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是大野…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.24,0:08:04.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被她的Cosplay迷惑了是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.11,0:08:05.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春日部
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.11,0:08:09.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…沒「那回素」啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.59,0:08:13.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春日部 不可以做出太過激的事哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.09,0:08:14.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們可是新人…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.92,0:08:18.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白啦 會長
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.06,0:08:22.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 奉勸你們還是別來這個社團為好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.03,0:08:27.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實這個房間會出現那種東西哦～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.27,0:08:31.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五年前去世的初代會長的鬼魂…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.61,0:08:34.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.14,0:08:36.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還活著啦 初代會長還活著
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.24,0:08:37.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不要隨便詛咒人家死啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.98,0:08:39.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有騙你們喔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.68,0:08:41.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我一直都沒提
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.08,0:08:43.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我有時候會看到他
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.28,0:08:45.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像是書架上的這種縫隙裏
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.25,0:08:47.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有張戴著眼鏡 長得像狗一樣的臉浮在半空中…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.79,0:08:50.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼說得好像跟真的一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.06,0:08:55.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們現在別回頭哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.00,0:08:59.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後面的書架的陰影處有一張人臉…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.07,0:09:01.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(註：此影像為想像畫面)
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.50,0:09:04.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說了 別說了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.37,0:09:06.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小笑 你演得真棒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.21,0:09:08.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.71,0:09:10.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是假的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.91,0:09:12.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天曉得
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.61,0:09:17.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我當初料想的一樣 春日部開始在整新人了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.25,0:09:19.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要想辦法阻止她
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.92,0:09:21.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.32,0:09:22.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以會長的身份
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.33,0:09:32.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 現代視覺文化研究會迎新餐會現在開始
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.67,0:09:34.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乾杯！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.07,0:09:35.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乾杯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.51,0:09:45.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不喝酒是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.65,0:09:46.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你不用勉強…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.31,0:09:49.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是在想 大家不一口氣幹掉嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.42,0:09:50.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會 不會
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.89,0:09:53.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊 真沒精神啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.52,0:09:54.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與其說沒精神
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.66,0:09:56.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不如說我們有我們的作風
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.49,0:09:57.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.53,0:09:59.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.63,0:10:00.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 很樂意為您服務
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.06,0:10:03.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春季蔬菜披薩
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.00,0:10:05.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手工蛋卷
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.73,0:10:07.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬆軟男爵可樂餅
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.54,0:10:08.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小籠包
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.94,0:10:10.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炸起司餛鈍 然後還要…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.81,0:10:11.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.87,0:10:14.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也要點嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.11,0:10:16.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫個組合套餐如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.78,0:10:19.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正是迎新餐會嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.61,0:10:22.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那就炸雞塊跟…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.75,0:10:24.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,NO！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.62,0:10:26.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人家不吃雞肉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.42,0:10:27.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反對炸雞塊！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.99,0:10:33.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那就取…取消炸雞塊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.63,0:10:35.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 樂意為您服務
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.20,0:10:38.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,換成…醃漬整…整條茄子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.63,0:10:40.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,YES
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.40,0:10:47.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們想看看中野的男子漢氣魄
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.34,0:10:47.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一口氣干了…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.88,0:10:50.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那件衣服的牌子是CECLL McBEE吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.88,0:10:50.37,Note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,CECLL McBEE：日本知名服裝品牌
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.61,0:10:53.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然很適合你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.62,0:10:55.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「果然」是什麼意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.05,0:10:59.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為很少有人可以穿出味道來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.42,0:11:00.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是熟人就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.02,0:11:03.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果第一次見面的男人就稱讚自己的衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.66,0:11:07.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會認為他另有企圖
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.19,0:11:09.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我並沒有那個意思啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.23,0:11:10.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒用的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.36,0:11:11.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.53,0:11:14.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來這裏只是為了盯住高阪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.90,0:11:17.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那樣子的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.87,0:11:20.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起來完全不像是那樣嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.47,0:11:21.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然是像哪樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.91,0:11:25.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們看起來只像是普通朋友…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.42,0:11:28.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟你無關吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.72,0:11:32.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 觸及到敏感話題了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.05,0:11:34.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先說清楚了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.66,0:11:37.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然這是迎新餐會 但我可一點都不歡迎你們
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.03,0:11:41.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別那麼說嘛 大家好好玩玩嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.10,0:11:42.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大野
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.36,0:11:43.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來想喝什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.87,0:11:47.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.33,0:11:48.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.74,0:11:49.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.04,0:11:51.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 很樂意為您服務
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.21,0:11:56.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該選哪個就照神的旨意吧～
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.38,0:12:00.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs26}兩個人的Heart Balance
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.78,0:12:00.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找點話題
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.55,0:12:03.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs26}不平衡抽籤
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.55,0:12:03.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你才是會…會長吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.45,0:12:04.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs26}無論是戀愛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.89,0:12:08.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs26}夢想還是憧憬
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.09,0:12:08.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朽…朽木
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.92,0:12:11.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼會選擇我們社團？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.93,0:12:13.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.09,0:12:15.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因為大野吧 大野的Cosplay
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.73,0:12:18.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是說好了不說這個的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.37,0:12:20.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了這個之外
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.07,0:12:22.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有沒有其它理由呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.94,0:12:24.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想想哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.74,0:12:26.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我還年幼時
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.01,0:12:31.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就對動漫畫抱持著濃厚深遠的興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.31,0:12:32.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再來想喝什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.11,0:12:32.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs26}但是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.78,0:12:34.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.78,0:12:34.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs26}在我國中跟高中時代
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.75,0:12:36.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑醋栗橘汁調酒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.75,0:12:36.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs26}由於經濟因素及顧慮社會目光
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.32,0:12:37.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.85,0:12:38.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 很樂意為您服務
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.85,0:12:38.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs26}一直無法參加正式的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.05,0:12:41.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…學術研究活動
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.29,0:12:42.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以打算利用進大學的機會 徹底改頭換面…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.02,0:12:46.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是春季蔬菜披薩以及鬆軟男爵可樂餅
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.93,0:12:47.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.53,0:12:49.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是人家的哦～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.90,0:12:55.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然自己獨佔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.74,0:12:57.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好delicious哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.47,0:13:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他想在大學改變個性是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.21,0:13:04.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不喝酒嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.41,0:13:06.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才沒那種事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.75,0:13:11.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啤酒對我來說就像水一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.25,0:13:13.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在高中時就常喝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.56,0:13:20.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我並不喜歡像漫研或動研那種OTAKU氣息很濃的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.39,0:13:22.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也都是OTAKU啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.90,0:13:25.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是這裏有女生社員
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.10,0:13:27.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光這點就完全不同了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.20,0:13:32.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實我也有到漫研去看過
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.37,0:13:34.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全待不下去嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.74,0:13:37.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全是些想叫他去死的醜胖子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.44,0:13:39.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個我就不清楚了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.52,0:13:44.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,動畫現在已經是日本的文化了不是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.95,0:13:47.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光只會享受末免也太蠢了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.72,0:13:50.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該要把它當成文化來研究…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.03,0:13:53.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說的「文化」的意思是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.93,0:13:57.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…次文化(subculture)嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.60,0:14:01.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 次文化 簡稱「次文」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.47,0:14:02.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.54,0:14:05.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在的劇場版動畫能到坎城影展參展
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.54,0:14:05.56,Note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法國坎城影展，每年5月舉行，國際所公認的一級影展之一
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.64,0:14:06.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,角色模型還被當成藝術品
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.84,0:14:09.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在蘇富比拍賣會上競標呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.61,0:14:12.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你懂得還真多
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.78,0:14:14.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些只能算是常識吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.92,0:14:17.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.18,0:14:18.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑醋栗橘汁調酒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.02,0:14:20.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑醋栗橘汁調酒？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.55,0:14:21.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.52,0:14:22.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我喝一口
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.36,0:14:27.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好喝～
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.83,0:14:29.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.66,0:14:30.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 很樂意為您服務
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.90,0:14:32.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑醋栗橘汁調酒…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.07,0:14:34.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 很樂意為您服務
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.27,0:14:39.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這杯我來喝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.07,0:14:40.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不要緊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.71,0:14:42.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑醋栗橘汁調酒 讓您久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.68,0:14:43.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.01,0:14:45.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 很樂意為您服務
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.18,0:14:47.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芋燒酒雙份加冰塊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.15,0:14:49.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 很樂意為您服務
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.38,0:14:51.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 我也要燒酒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.05,0:14:53.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 很樂意為您服務
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.29,0:14:55.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近很流行喝燒酒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.82,0:14:58.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的燒酒甚至比日本酒還要美味
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.53,0:15:00.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那樣的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.46,0:15:03.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我雖然這副德行 但對流行可是很敏感的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.50,0:15:05.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,改天一起去喝好喝的燒酒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.87,0:15:07.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會先把店找好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.64,0:15:08.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.01,0:15:12.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去一下廁所
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.91,0:15:21.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聚餐嗎？真是難得
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.15,0:15:23.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是迎新餐會啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.12,0:15:24.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.62,0:15:25.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有幾個人加入？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.89,0:15:28.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩個 不過只是暫時加入的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.19,0:15:30.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真少啊 現視研撐得下去嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.93,0:15:34.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漫研雖然訂了包廂 但還是擠得要命
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.43,0:15:36.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都鬧得可瘋了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.43,0:15:38.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我聽說了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.47,0:15:41.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你當上會長了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.24,0:15:44.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為不知不覺就變成我…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.14,0:15:49.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算來找我 我也會因為太忙而回絕的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.41,0:15:52.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 好歹也該問我一聲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.98,0:15:54.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.75,0:15:58.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也算是現視研的監護人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.15,0:16:01.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遇到麻煩就跟我說一聲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.49,0:16:03.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會幫你的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.33,0:16:14.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大野
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.00,0:16:16.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.47,0:16:17.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.97,0:16:19.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小笑 你要不要也喝一口？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.01,0:16:21.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.71,0:16:26.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是酒桶嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.31,0:16:29.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為自己是OTAKU而自暴自棄的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.82,0:16:32.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不覺得這種人是最讓人看不下去的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.62,0:16:34.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家並沒有自暴自…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.32,0:16:36.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裏沒有？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.59,0:16:38.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我總覺得…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.13,0:16:40.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還好吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.96,0:16:42.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我陪他去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.76,0:16:44.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼是高阪去？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.67,0:16:46.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿屜陪他去不就好了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.21,0:16:56.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小笑 請喝一口吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.44,0:16:57.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是說我不喝嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.95,0:16:59.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大野 你會不會喝太多了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.75,0:17:01.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是在為我擔心嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.38,0:17:04.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好喜歡小笑哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.85,0:17:05.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.49,0:17:10.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能跟你一起喝酒真幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.09,0:17:11.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒喝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.63,0:17:13.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有你在喝啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.96,0:17:15.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你也一起喝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.96,0:17:18.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不太喜歡喝燒酒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.73,0:17:21.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 我可以陪你喝啤酒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.00,0:17:24.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好喜歡小笑喔～
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.84,0:17:26.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.24,0:17:27.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,東西別忘了拿
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.54,0:17:30.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs26}兩個人的Heart Balance
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.51,0:17:33.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs26}不平衡抽籤
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.48,0:17:37.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs26}無論是戀愛 夢想還是憧憬…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.79,0:17:40.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還好吧 要不要我去幫你倒杯水？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.69,0:17:43.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好得很 沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.99,0:17:47.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小笑 喝吧喝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.69,0:17:49.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…我有在喝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.03,0:17:51.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多喝一點
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.00,0:17:53.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就饒了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.93,0:17:55.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朽朽 吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.44,0:17:58.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本店最後點餐的時間就要過了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.94,0:18:00.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問還要點些什麼嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.41,0:18:02.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小笑 你真的不要緊嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.51,0:18:04.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 我在喝了…不要緊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.61,0:18:06.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.08,0:18:07.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很樂意為您服務
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.48,0:18:10.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,田中 要…要回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.85,0:18:13.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,澤崎 你的臉色發青哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.89,0:18:17.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs26}兩個人的Heart Ba…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.99,0:18:17.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人家要去便便
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.39,0:18:19.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝惠顧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.40,0:18:24.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還好吧 你的臉色還是不太好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.23,0:18:26.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我已經沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.60,0:18:29.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦？就此解散嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.20,0:18:32.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再去續攤嘛 續攤好不好？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.77,0:18:33.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.91,0:18:35.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還想繼續跟大家在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.88,0:18:37.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是每家店都打烊了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.11,0:18:40.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那要不要來我家？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.02,0:18:44.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己隨便找地方坐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.65,0:18:46.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.09,0:18:47.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確很打擾
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.66,0:18:54.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs26}高…高阪 漫畫借我看好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.66,0:18:54.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說你這個新人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.83,0:18:56.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是別人的房間吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.13,0:18:59.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼關係 反正都是同一個社團的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.27,0:19:01.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只是暫時加入的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.87,0:19:04.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我挺喜歡這裏的 要我正式加入也可以哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.40,0:19:05.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我也喝茶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.81,0:19:06.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斑目呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.61,0:19:07.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要喝可樂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.91,0:19:09.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就來進行測試吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.51,0:19:11.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,入社測試
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.85,0:19:14.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果玩那個叫什麼格鬥遊戲的 你能夠打贏高阪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.02,0:19:16.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就讓你加入如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.78,0:19:18.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個主意不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.05,0:19:20.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也蠻喜歡玩格鬥遊戲的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.05,0:19:22.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不錯哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.46,0:19:23.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要來玩看看？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.82,0:19:25.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就來玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.23,0:19:26.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勸你還是不要
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.49,0:19:27.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是說真的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.39,0:19:27.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.03,0:19:29.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玩吧 玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.20,0:19:31.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,順便培養感情 我會手下留情的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.43,0:19:35.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用不著手下留情 照你平常的打法就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.47,0:19:39.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要跟上次玩「噗呦噗呦!」那時一樣的水準喔！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.57,0:19:40.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.01,0:19:44.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「Guilty Gear Isuka」啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.01,0:19:44.00,Note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「Guilty Gear Isuka」：罪惡裝備Isuka
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.08,0:19:45.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個才剛出的對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.91,0:19:47.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是不是常去玩大型機台的？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.71,0:19:48.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.52,0:19:52.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,越愛耍酷的傢伙功力越弱
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.72,0:19:53.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看我好好教訓教訓你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.20,0:20:09.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扔起來然後直接在空中連續攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.14,0:20:11.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高阪 你是哪個？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.51,0:20:12.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男生的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.51,0:20:16.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的強制取消被他給識破了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.68,0:20:18.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然從DUST發動D Loop
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.89,0:20:25.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.79,0:20:26.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高阪贏了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.92,0:20:28.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個遊戲只有一回戰
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.62,0:20:29.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要再比一場？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.73,0:20:39.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.04,0:20:44.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贏了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.94,0:20:47.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是是 他贏了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.48,0:20:52.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然是打遊戲 不過男友贏了還是很高興嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.25,0:20:54.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.51,0:20:56.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的程度還不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.32,0:20:59.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩場都徹底輸給了你 你居然還這樣說
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.19,0:21:01.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 因為你喝了酒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.36,0:21:02.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.76,0:21:04.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你完全沒喝半滴酒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.73,0:21:07.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而我卻灌了不少
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.13,0:21:09.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你會這麼強也是理所當然的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.20,0:21:10.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要再打一場嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.10,0:21:11.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然要
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.40,0:21:12.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.43,0:21:13.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.60,0:21:14.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要去幫他打氣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.37,0:21:17.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高阪 加油
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.37,0:21:19.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春日部 這麼多人在看耶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.31,0:21:21.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一場也贏的話 我就親你一下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.84,0:21:23.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.08,0:21:25.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你幹嘛從剛才起就一直大吼大叫的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.31,0:21:26.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我當然會叫了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.41,0:21:29.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要親…親他 與測試無關吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.82,0:21:30.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,測試是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.02,0:21:32.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像有那麼回事哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.65,0:21:35.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.19,0:21:38.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要能打贏高阪 就算是新人我也親你一下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.09,0:21:41.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小笑你又來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.57,0:21:55.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一堂課在哪裏上？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.22,0:22:08.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.22,0:22:09.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我記得他好像是…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.59,0:22:15.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不曉得你是否還記得
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.93,0:22:18.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小時候的…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.17,0:22:26.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪裏？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.61,0:22:32.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.95,0:22:34.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高阪都不會不舒服嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.05,0:22:36.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全不會
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.82,0:22:37.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.98,0:22:38.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.92,0:22:41.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是在想說 只要每年都讓高阪進行測試
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.19,0:22:43.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就可以讓現視研關門大吉咯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.09,0:22:45.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧 會長
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.04,0:24:43.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,屜原 你對妹妹型的沒興趣對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.94,0:24:46.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我比較喜歡的應該是青梅竹馬型吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.41,0:24:48.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那女僕呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.08,0:24:48.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.85,0:24:50.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有 雖然現在說這個有點老套
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.62,0:24:52.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 貓耳可是基本配備
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.52,0:24:54.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我比較喜歡繃帶少女
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.29,0:24:55.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人前人後是兩種個性的班長類型呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.79,0:24:56.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.36,0:24:59.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道有沒有角色扮演遊戲或動畫裏面有那種角色的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.36,0:25:01.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青梅竹馬的貓耳女僕
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.26,0:25:03.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在學校是班長 平時態度嚴肅
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.80,0:25:05.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但做事常常很迷糊 渾身纏滿繃帶
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.43,0:25:06.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人在的時候完全不理男主角 沒人在的時候則緊纏著不放
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.87,0:25:09.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好萌啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.18,0:25:09.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(352,266)}量產型製造過程的比較研究
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.90,0:00:23.60,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}朝起きて　例によって　携帯忘れて　乗り遅れた
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.68,0:00:29.48,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}鈍行の窓に映る人生
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.61,0:00:34.28,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}日本中で誰にも負けない一つがあるにはあるけど
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.35,0:00:39.38,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\an7}悲しいかな　人知れず
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.19,0:00:42.96,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}だけども速くは走れない
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.03,0:00:45.50,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}そんなに丈夫にできてない
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.56,0:00:52.47,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\an7}いざ行け　不屈のマイペース
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.57,0:00:58.91,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}今日の悲しみよ過ぎ去ってゆけ天気雨
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.98,0:01:01.54,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}二の足　二の舞
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.61,0:01:04.24,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}一夜一夜に夢見頃
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.32,0:01:09.58,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}さらば悲しみよ大気圏の外へ出ろ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.65,0:01:15.15,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}上空めがけて大きな声を張り上げろ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.26,0:01:18.42,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}このテンポで
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.80,0:01:28.80,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}今　このテンポで
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.90,0:00:23.60,OP_CH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}早上起床依舊忘了手機　趕不上電車
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.68,0:00:29.48,OP_CH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}映照在慢車窗戶上的人生
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.61,0:00:34.28,OP_CH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}雖然也有不輸人的日本第一
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.35,0:00:39.38,OP_CH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\an3}但很悲哀無人知曉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.19,0:00:42.96,OP_CH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}雖然跑得不快
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.03,0:00:45.50,OP_CH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}長得也不太強壯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.56,0:00:52.47,OP_CH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\an3}向前衝吧　不認輸的我行我素
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.57,0:00:58.91,OP_CH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}今天的悲傷啊　快快過去吧　太陽雨
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.98,0:01:01.54,OP_CH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}躊躇不前　重蹈覆轍
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.61,0:01:04.24,OP_CH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}每晚每晚好作夢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.32,0:01:09.58,OP_CH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}再會了哀傷　滾到大氣層外頭
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.65,0:01:15.15,OP_CH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}朝著天空大聲吶喊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.26,0:01:18.42,OP_CH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}用這個節奏
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.80,0:01:28.80,OP_CH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}現在用這個節奏
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.87,0:23:15.57,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\frz270\q2}遠回りも近道もしないで僕らは
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.08,0:23:25.65,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\frz270\q2}明日がくることを　怖がる事もなくて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.72,0:23:33.86,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\frz270\q2}歩き続けた　深夜の井の頭通り
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.86,0:23:44.50,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\frz270\q2}鮮やかな夢だけ　長く影に延びた
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.51,0:23:53.81,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\frz270\q2}大人未満の僕らは
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.92,0:24:06.35,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\frz270\q2}単純で難解な煌めくびいだま
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.43,0:24:10.89,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\frz270\q2}そこから覗いていた時間が
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.97,0:24:15.60,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\frz270\q2}たいしたものはなくたって　輝いてたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.67,0:24:20.13,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\frz270\q2}今　この手の中にあるびいだまから
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.21,0:24:25.98,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\frz270\q2}見えるものは　少し違うけど
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.05,0:24:34.89,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\frz270\q2}僕らのそばで　小さく光ってる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.87,0:23:15.57,ED_CH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\frz270\q2}我們不抄近路　也不走遠路
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.08,0:23:25.65,ED_CH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\frz270\q2}也不畏懼明天的到來
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.72,0:23:33.86,ED_CH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\frz270\q2}持續走在深夜的井之頭大道
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.86,0:23:44.50,ED_CH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\frz270\q2}只有繽紛的夢想　延伸出長長的影子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.51,0:23:53.81,ED_CH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\frz270\q2}尚未長大成人的我們
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.92,0:24:06.35,ED_CH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\frz270\q2}是既單純又難解的耀眼彈珠
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.43,0:24:10.89,ED_CH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\frz270\q2}從那裏窺探到的時間
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.97,0:24:15.60,ED_CH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\frz270\q2}即使並不稀奇　卻也閃閃發光
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.67,0:24:20.13,ED_CH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\frz270\q2}現在從手中的彈珠裏
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.21,0:24:25.98,ED_CH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\frz270\q2}看到的景象雖然有些不同
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.05,0:24:34.89,ED_CH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\frz270\q2}卻就在我們的身邊　微弱地散發著光芒

